text: Zus Engelenberg (4 January 1909 - 16 May 1984) was a South African swimmer. She competed in the women's 100 metre freestyle event at the 1928 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1909 births Category:1984 deaths Category:South African female swimmers Category:Olympic swimmers of South Africa Category:Swimmers at the 1928 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Pretoria Category:South African female freestyle swimmers
